OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright, but rather cool day
OL,6,Fwith some good spells of sunshine and
OL,7,Fa few showers around, more especially
OL,8,Facross Orkney. Light and variable
OL,9,Fwinds, becoming more northerly this
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,13,Fclear spells overnight, with showers.
OL,14,FThe showers, especially across Orkney,
OL,15,Fbecoming more frequent and
OL,16,Foccasionally heavy through the early
OL,17,Fhours. Strengthening northerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
