OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA breezy and rather cold day
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers, most
OL,7,Ffrequent and occasionally heavy across
OL,8,FOrkney in the morning. Strong
OL,9,Fnortherly winds, risk of gales for
OL,10,FShetland later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,13,Fspells and showers Friday, northerly
OL,14,Fwinds easing. Risk of the odd shower
OL,15,FSaturday but mainly dry and bright.
OL,16,FSunday, Orkney rather cloudy with some
OL,17,Frain, Shetland dry and bright.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
